<div><div><h2>Icra downgrades IDFC Bank</h2></div><div>"domestic ratings agency icra has downgraded the long-term ratings of the youngest private sector lender idfc bank on profitability concerns.downgrading the bank the agency said profitability of the bank will remain weak in the medium- to near- term even after the planned merger with capital first and added that high cost wholesale liabilities are also a concern."</div></div>